  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\"><img alt=\"Braavos.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a2/Braavos.svg/50px-Braavos.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a2/Braavos.svg/75px-Braavos.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a2/Braavos.svg/100px-Braavos.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Narha Otherys</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\"><img alt=\"Braavos.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a2/Braavos.svg/50px-Braavos.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a2/Braavos.svg/75px-Braavos.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a2/Braavos.svg/100px-Braavos.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Narha_Otherys_by_Riotarttherite.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Narha Otherys by Riotarttherite.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/80/Narha_Otherys_by_Riotarttherite.jpg/350px-Narha_Otherys_by_Riotarttherite.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"389\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/80/Narha_Otherys_by_Riotarttherite.jpg/525px-Narha_Otherys_by_Riotarttherite.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/80/Narha_Otherys_by_Riotarttherite.jpg/700px-Narha_Otherys_by_Riotarttherite.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Narha Otherys, by riotarttherite ©</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Otherys\" title=\"House Otherys\">House Otherys</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\">Braavosi</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_162_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">162</a>–<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_171_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">171&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Father</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_IV_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon IV Targaryen\">Aegon IV Targaryen</a> <small>(disputed)</small></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Mother</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Bellegere_Otherys\" title=\"Bellegere Otherys\">Bellegere Otherys</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Narha Otherys</b> was the second of the three <a href=\"/index.php/Bastard\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bastard\">bastard</a> children of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_IV_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon IV Targaryen\">Aegon IV Targaryen</a> and his fourth mistress, <a href=\"/index.php/Bellegere_Otherys\" title=\"Bellegere Otherys\">Bellegere Otherys</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf411.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf411.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Narha_Otherys&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>After Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Naerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Naerys Targaryen\">Naerys Targaryen</a> had almost died, giving birth in <a href=\"/index.php/161_AC\" title=\"161 AC\">161&#160;AC</a>, her husband, Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_IV_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon IV Targaryen\">Aegon</a> was send to <a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\">Braavos</a> as an envoy, so Naerys would have sufficient time to recover. In Braavos, Aegon met Bellegere Otherys, with whom he started an affair. Aegon and Bellegere had an affair for ten years, during which Bellegere gave birth to three children: <a href=\"/index.php/Bellenora_Otherys\" title=\"Bellenora Otherys\">Bellenora</a>, Narha and <a href=\"/index.php/Balerion_Otherys\" title=\"Balerion Otherys\">Balerion</a>. Their paternity remains doubtful, as Bellegere is said to have had a husband in every port she visited.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf411.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf411.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Narha_Otherys&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Sealord\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Sealord\">Sealord<br />Otherys</a></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px